title: attachments()
brief: Return a table of attachment-names.
seealso: attachment_colour, count_attachments, save_attachment
version: 0.10
----

<p>This function will return a table containing the names of any attachments in the currently selected mesage.</p>
<p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
a = attachments();

-- for each attachment
for index,name in ipairs( a ) do
    -- Save it into /tmp with the same name
    save_attachment( i, "/tmp/" .. name );
end
</pre>


